  "texts": [
    "People envision that providing a brief description of a software project will enable LLMs to automatically generate a fully functional software system.",
    "However, LLMs are not mind readers.",
    "A critical aspect of leveraging LLMs is the quality of the input.",
    "In the context of software development, that input would be the requirements.",
    "The potential of the LLMs to generate effective code hinges on the details and clarity of the requirements documents."
  ],
